itemDescription: Member of the Romanov family and president of the Romanov Family Association

wikipedia_page.main: Princess Olga Andreevna Romanoff (Russian: О́льга Андре́евна Рома́нова, romanized: Ólga Andréevna Románova; born 8 April 1950) is a Russian princess and descendant of the House of Romanov. She is the president of the Romanov Family Association.
